Shri Mataji: Yes.
Interviewer: And he was able to also feel the cool breeze
Shri Mataji: Yes, yes. And also from the [hands]
Interviewer: Can you give me the cool breeze? I've been waiting all my life for that.
Shri Mataji: Yes, I think you pass
