Shri Mataji: No, no, no, no. It might help, talking to me you might get it, but actually you feel it on your fingertips.  As Muhammad Sahib has said that: "At the time of Resurection your hands will speak." And for the first time you feel that All-pervading subtle power, that you become something more than what you are.
That's the saint.

